<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَغْشَى}</span> ... يُغَطِّي بِظَلَامِهِ الأَرْضَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَجَلَّى}</span> ... انْكَشَفَ بِضِيَائِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَشَتَّى}</span> ... لَمُخْتَلِفٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَعْطَى}</span> ... بَذَلَ مَالَهُ مُتَصَدِّقًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْحُسْنَى}</span> ... بِالثَّوَابِ عَلَى أَعْمَالِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِلْيُسْرَى}</span> ... لِكُلِّ خَيْرٍ، وَسَعَادَةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِلْعُسْرَى}</span> ... لِكُلِّ عُسْرٍ، وَشَقَاوَةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا يُغْنِي}</span> ... لَا يَنْفَعُهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَرَدَّى}</span> ... وَقَعَ فِي النَّارِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا لَلْهُدَى}</span> ... عَلَيْنَا أَنْ نُبَيِّنَ طَرِيقَ الهُدَى؛ فَضْلًا مِنَّا وَرَحْمَةً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَلَظَّى}</span> ... تَتَوَهَّجُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يَصْلَاهَا}</span> ... لَا يَدْخُلُهَا، وَيُقَاسِي حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا}</span> ... سَيُبْعَدُ عَنْهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُجْزَى}</span> ... تُكَافَأُ؛ فَلَيْسَ إِنْفَاقُهُ مُكَافَأَةً لِمَنْ أَحْسَنَ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>